=======Requirements========
lazarus >= 0.9.26
gcc >= 4.5.2
linux >=2.6.26
=======Compile & Install==========
open the terminal, type
	make
to compile. 
when the compilation is successfully done, type
	sudo make install
to install SILICA to your macine.
type
	sudo make remove
to remove SILICA from your machine.


for more information, check the documentation in the 'doc' directory.

if you have any question, please contact yanchengyuan@gmail.com

